name: Salmon Couscous & Arugula Salad
description: Roasted salmon is served on a bed of arugula with organic cucumbers, couscous, grape tomatoes, and olives. A dressing of citrus honey mustard is served on the side.
reviews: Good, but be nice to have a little more salmon!
Salmon way undercooked. Ridiculously dangerous for delivery food, so I had to set it aside. I feel completely ripped off!
Slimey. Not how I hope to describe my food.
